{"tid":1633775,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Samsung 將解散 CPU 核心架構部門並轉向類似高通的半客製化 Cortex-A 方案","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:13:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T06:20:20.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ff5fcc64eac382a7a0bccf479d827c64ab3f080f","tid":1633775,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:13:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cool3c.com/article/148624\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cool3c.com%2Farticle%2F148624&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4jr7MFgrQ0V0XG6LyL0fmAc%3D&h=a8bd8aac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cool3c.com/article/148624</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然 Arm 提供的 Cortex-A 核心架構是當前市場上許多晶片開發商選擇的架構，不過或許是由於蘋果採用 Arm 微指令集開發的自主架構表現優異，如高通、三星等也紛紛投入客製化核心開發，不過即便指令集擺在眼前，把這些指令集構成自主核心仍不容易，隨著高通近年轉向基於 Cortex-A 的 Kryo 半客製化架構後，現在也傳出三星在歷經十年的自主核心開發後，有意解散位於德州奧斯丁的自主核心架構研發部門，並採取與高通類似的半客製化核心方案或 Arm 的 Cortex-A 公版方案。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://sw.cool3c.com/r/card/user/29442/2019/a56507e7-d250-4539-b44b-737616d51376.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsw.cool3c.com%2Fr%2Fcard%2Fuser%2F29442%2F2019%2Fa56507e7-d250-4539-b44b-737616d51376.jpg&h=e4afb15d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三星開發自主核心 Mongoose 已經進入第四代，不過不要說能否追上蘋果自行設計的核心表現，甚至也跟不上高通與 Arm 合作的 Kryo 半客製化方案，在多核性能、熱管理等皆遜於高通半客製化方案，這也讓三星思索放棄自主設計 CPU 架構一途。"},{"pid":"cb158bb42cff27f912d2057e59499c89bee4d5ba","tid":1633775,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:14:39.000Z","msg":"不過這並非表示三星會減緩自主高階平台的開發，三星接下來據傳可能會直接擁抱高通的 Cortex-A 標準設計，或是如高通一樣與 Arm 合作，由 Arm 為其操刀半客製化核心設計，另外在 GPU 則結合 AMD 提供的 RDNA Radeon GPU 架構，透過專利組合方式使核心的基本盤更為強勢並且具備差異化。<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.androidcentral.com/new-report-says-samsung-ditching-custom-cpu-cores-arm-designs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.androidcentral.com%2Fnew-report-says-samsung-ditching-custom-cpu-cores-arm-designs&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4jr7MFgrQ0V0XG6LyL0fmAc%3D&h=e595612c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.androidcentral.com/new-report-says-samsung-ditching-custom-cpu-cores-arm-designs</a>"},{"pid":"4c039df451f1b6c738f616f69a362dfea58239a2","tid":1633775,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:30:46.000Z","msg":"有D野應該外判就要外判 好似制程team"},{"pid":"0d78afbc47cea8abda4555d094e978aa02fb1d99","tid":1633775,"uid":255744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:20:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}